createPool creates pool which integrate with compound's staking
 _startDate is date of starting pool, from this date pool's functions enable
 _participationEndDate is date after which the play function is not available
 _endDate is date of pool's end, enable to choose winner after this date
 _poolCost is required amount for participation

play spends user money to compound mint
 _pool is address of pool

setWinner set pool's winner, redeem all assets from compound
 _pool is address of pool

claim transfer asset from selt to user, winner also receive additional reward
